description: Loft-style PH duplex in South Boston's trendiest neighborhood. High ceilings, bamboo floors, custom built-ins and oversized windows. Sun-filled main level offering living room, stylish dining area, and gourmet kitchen complete with premium stainless appliances. There is a balcony off the kitchen. Upper level includes an en-suite primary bedroom, in-unit laundry & custom closets. There is an open-concept 2nd bedroom space with ample natural light sourced from skylight. This space is ideal for a home office or guest bedroom. Large private outdoor deck perfect for sun tanning, sunsets, and al fresco dining with friends. Heated garage parking, bike storage & storage. The most convenient commuter location in Boston! Quick access to highways and all Logan terminals. The Broadway T stop (Red line) and Amtrak/South Station are close. Minutes to Starbucks, Whole Foods, and many great Southie, South End, and Fort Point restaurants. Seller will entertain requests to pay buyer closing credits.
